    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's really intense and definitely hits the mark for the character. To finish the monologue, can you have him conclude by explaining why it's actually a moral necessity for his people to take control of the land and its resources, rather than leaving it to the locals? Maybe mention how their natural state is basically a waste of what the land could be if managed properly.",
